{"tid":1658070,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點對付美心！","createTime":"2019-10-16T11:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T11:26:11.000Z","uid":313923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d74a83981b0251195da737760da5530c01662024","tid":1658070,"uid":313923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:19:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nytimes/status/1184344479932801024?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnytimes%2Fstatus%2F1184344479932801024%3Fs%3D21&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Sry2VlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=0bb71258\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnytimes%2Fstatus%2F1184344479932801024%3Fs%3D21&h=a9ba9d8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/nytimes/status/1184344479932801024?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n美心大股東係牛奶國際，而牛奶國際母公司係怡和Jardine，一閒老牌英國洋行！<br />\n怡和一早就唔信共產黨，未回歸就已經放棄香港上市地位，東南亞改在新加坡上市！<br />\n怡和（東印公司）滿清晚年一直向中國輸出鴉片，換句話說，他亦有份引發鴉片戰爭，令滿清簽下南京條約，割讓香港予大英帝國，才有今天的香港！<br />\n怡和集團旗下置地（Hong Kong Land)是中環核心地帶大地主，擁有交易廣場、歷山大廈、置地廣場等中環名廈，很多港資中資對置地中環的土地大廈虎視眈眈，只要置地肯賣，可以話幾多錢共産黨都肯卑！如果怡和覺得在港受針對，有局勢不穩可能，趁依家個市未冧前出售果啲名廈比共產黨都唔出奇！<br />\n<br />\n傷害美心集團，最大損失不是姓伍個老西，而係怡和！我諗大家都唔想果啲名廈改曬名，如歷山大廈就改叫習帝大廈、置地廣場改叫天安門廣場、太子廣場改叫上海廣場、㵂打行改叫萬壽行等呱！<br />\n又用另一面睇，老西都只係用口講衰我哋，咁用手回敬又好似唔係大好，如此唔通用言語傷害我地就出手，咁咪要幫好多公司裝修？<br />\n幫福建360裝修我冇意見，因為721！<br />\n幫中資裝修我理解，因為背後主䐉係共匪，即係黑狗指揮！<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得應該點樣對付美心，自己諗一諗吧！"},{"pid":"407d68a531549c01875d1e77d6721458b37b9f44","tid":1658070,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:20:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">我要見到文宣砌成o既10.20 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S6T4n3o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS6T4n3o.jpg&h=dfdf4b42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【再次有圖有真相】令街坊知道1020遊行嘅最佳方法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1657842\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1657842</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d6f7b3932d72190262b005914a890205d035ce","tid":1658070,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:20:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD1QUeo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD1QUeo.jpg&h=564aedde&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"3ba6ab14297fc4978219b0f13db5c65e7b34e3f5","tid":1658070,"uid":128569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T11:26:11.000Z","msg":"食窮佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}